jobDescription.text:
Job Title: Forklift Operator

We are seeking a dedicated Forklift Operator to join our dynamic team. In this role, you will play a crucial part in maintaining our high standards of excellence in warehouse operations.

Location: Atlanta, GA

Salary: $17 to $20 USD Per Hour

Roles and Responsibilities:- Operate forklifts safely and efficiently to move materials and products throughout the warehouse.
- Load and unload goods from trucks and containers, ensuring accuracy and attention to detail.
- Conduct routine inspections of equipment to maintain safety and operational standards.
- Collaborate with team members to ensure optimal workflow and productivity.
- Maintain a clean and organized work environment to promote safety and efficiency.
- Adhere to all safety protocols and procedures to minimize risk and ensure a safe workplace.

Experience Level: Preferred experience level is 3 to 5 years.

Company Working Hours: 7 to 9 hours Per Day

Desired Skills:You should possess strong attention to detail and excellent communication skills, enabling effective collaboration with team members. A solid understanding of safety regulations and best practices in warehouse operations is essential. You are expected to demonstrate reliability and a strong work ethic, ensuring tasks are completed accurately and efficiently. Proficiency in operating various types of forklifts and equipment is necessary to succeed in this role.

Employment Type: Direct Hire

Company Description:** TRC Talent Solutions is proud to be an Equal Opportunity Employer (EOE). All qualified applicants will receive consideration for employment without regard to race, color, religion, sex, age, national origin, protected veteran status, disability status, sexual orientation, gender identity or expression, marital status, genetic information, or any other characteristic protected by law.

At TRC, we take pride in fulfilling our opportunity to add value to our clients business as their staffing partner, while working tirelessly to connect thousands of individuals each year with work opportunities where they can meet the needs of their families and have the potential to build their careers.
